description:
Aspose.BarCode for .NET is a robust and reliable barcode generation and recognition component, written in managed C#, it allows developers to quickly and easily add barcode generation and recognition functionality to their Microsoft .NET applications (WinForms, ASP.NET and .NET Compact Framework). 

Aspose.BarCode for .NET supports most established barcode standards and barcode specifications. It has the ability to export to multiple image formats including: BMP, EMF, GIF, JPEG, PNG, TIFF and WMF.
releaseNotes:
The following is a list of improvements and improvements and changes in this release of Aspose.BarCode.

Major features
We have greatly reworked the BarCode project and now we support recognition in WPF targeted assemblies (BARCODENET-33815).

Other Improvements and Changes
New Features
BARCODENET-33800 Aspose.BarCode API support for .NET Compact Framework 3.5
BARCODENET-33851 Merge recognition and generation modules

Enhancements
BARCODENET-33697 Code128 not found with 5.8
BARCODENET-33766 Reduce DataMatrix barcode image (jpg) size
BARCODENET-33776 Reading two EAN13 barcodes instead of one from a pdf file
BARCODENET-33777 Can't recognize Code128 codes from a PDF file
BARCODENET-33778 Can't recognize Code128 and PDF417 codes from specific pages of a PDF file
BARCODENET-33779 Add resolution support to GetCustomSizeBarCodeImage and GetOnlyBarCodeImage methods
BARCODENET-33783 Improve recognition of barcode inside a frame
BARCODENET-33785 Datamatrix barcode is not recognizable
BARCODENET-33786 Australia Post EParcel barcode is missed with corresponding symbology
BARCODENET-33788 Can't recognize Code128 and DataMatrix codes from a tif file format
BARCODENET-33798 Can't recognize 8th Code39 symbology from each tif image
BARCODENET-33814 Dual sign the .Net assembly

Bugs
BARCODENET-33780 Last digit is missed during recognition for PLANET and POSTNET symbologies
BARCODENET-33782 Onecode recognition for test file is broken
BARCODENET-33801 Black line appears on the right side of rotated Interleaved2of5 barcode
BARCODENET-33803 Incorrect Code 128 recognition from a jpg image
summary: Aspose.BarCode for .NET is a robust and reliable barcode generation and recognition component
title: Aspose.BarCode for .NET
